OL,3,CNew York declares state of emergency
OL,4,Cafter 'heart attack snow' and high
OL,5,Cwinds
OL,7,FMillions in New York City were stuck
OL,8,Fat home on Monday after a travel ban
OL,9,Fcaused by "heart attack snow" and high
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,12,FAs blizzard warnings stretched from
OL,13,FMaryland to Maine, some areas of the
OL,14,Fnortheast US have had over a foot of
OL,15,Fsnow since Sunday, along with wind
OL,16,Fgusts of over 30 mph and low
OL,17,Fvisibility.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
