PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771858066
OL,3,CNew York declares state of emergency
OL,4,Cafter 'heart attack snow' and high
OL,5,Cwinds
OL,7,FMobile phones across New York received
OL,8,Femergency alerts, preventing non-
OL,9,Femergency travel on all streets from
OL,10,Fmidday due to "dangerous blizzard
OL,11,Fconditions."
OL,13,FIt is the first time in nine years
OL,14,Fthat New York City has been under a
OL,15,Fblizzard warning.
OL,17,FThe National Weather Service called
OL,18,Ftravel conditions "nearly impossible",
OL,19,Fas the historic storm triggered power-
OL,20,Fcuts as well as public travel
OL,21,Fcancellations and delays.
