OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771858066
OL,3,CNew York declares state of emergency
OL,4,Cafter 'heart attack snow' and high
OL,5,Cwinds
OL,7,FA state of emergency was also declared
OL,8,Fin Delaware, New Jersey,
OL,9,FMassachusetts, and Rhode Island, with
OL,10,Fofficials in several states urging
OL,11,Fpeople to avoid venturing out.
OL,13,FMore than 5,000 flights in and out of
OL,14,Fthe United States were canceled for
OL,15,FMonday, with New York City and Boston
OL,16,Fseeing the most cancellations and
OL,17,Fdelays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
