OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771858066
OL,3,CNew York declares state of emergency
OL,4,Cafter 'heart attack snow' and high
OL,5,Cwinds
OL,7,FBoth cities have shut public schools
OL,8,Ffor Monday, with New York Mayor Zohran
OL,9,FMamdani calling it the "first old-
OL,10,Fschool snow day since 2019."
OL,12,FWeather service meteorologist Frank
OL,13,FPereira said the storm could become a
OL,14,Fbomb cyclone, which is when a storm
OL,15,Fdrops at least 24 millibars in
OL,16,Fpressure in 24 hours.
OL,26,@qD@XOUrD@\O]
