PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771858066
OL,3,CNew York declares state of emergency
OL,4,Cafter 'heart attack snow' and high
OL,5,Cwinds
OL,7,F"We expect things to dramatically
OL,8,Fchange here" heading into the
OL,9,Fovernight, weather service
OL,10,Fmeteorologist Frank Pereira said
OL,11,FSunday.
OL,13,F"The storm is continuing to develop,
OL,14,Fand as it does, as it continues to
OL,15,Fstrengthen and move to the north,
OL,16,Fwe're expecting conditions to rapidly
OL,17,Fdeteriorate."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@LO]uD@AOUyD@MO]
