OL,3,CNew York declares state of emergency
OL,4,Cafter 'heart attack snow' and high
OL,5,Cwinds
OL,7,FPereira added that the storm could
OL,8,Fbecome a bomb cyclone, which is when a
OL,9,Fstorm drops at least 24 millibars in
OL,10,Fpressure in 24 hours.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning. https:/
OL,16,F/itvnews.substack.com/
OL,18,FSome have dubbed the snow "heart
OL,19,Fattack snow", as experts remind people
OL,20,Fto shovel wet snow with caution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
