PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771858066
OL,3,CNew York declares state of emergency
OL,4,Cafter 'heart attack snow' and high
OL,5,Cwinds
OL,7,FPrevious advice from Harvard Health
OL,8,FPublishing states: "Picking up a
OL,9,Fshovel and moving hundreds of pounds
OL,10,Fof snow, particularly after doing
OL,11,Fnothing physical for several months,
OL,12,Fcan put a big strain on the heart."
OL,14,FThey add: "Cold weather is another
OL,15,Fcontributor because it can boost blood
OL,16,Fpressure, interrupt blood flow to part
OL,17,Fof the heart, and make blood more
OL,18,Flikely to form clots."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
